Description: Secure VPN gateway web control center
A PHP-based VPN gateway dashboard for selecting outbound OpenVPN profiles,
monitoring tunnel state, and providing local-route fallback controls.
.
This package installs the gateway web application, vpnadmin helper script,
and rsyslog integration snippet for OpenVPN runtime logs.
